author: Seneca
message: Most powerful is he who has himself in his own power.
title: Thought of the day

author: Bernard Shaw
message: We don't stop playing because we grow old; we grow old because we stop playing.
title: Thought of the day

author: Byron Pulsifer
message: Experience can only be gained by doing not by thinking or dreaming.
title: Thought of the day

author: Mark Twain
message: Always tell the truth. That way, you don't have to remember what you said.
title: Thought of the day
